high_descs: Turn around and then take a right before turning to face right
Pick up a pepper grinder off of the counter
Turn around from your position
Open a cabinet and put the grinder into the cabinet
Turn around from your position
Pick up another pepper grinder off of the counter
Turn around from your position again
Open a cabinet and put other the grinder into the cabinet

Turn around and face the cabinets below the counter to the right of the stove.
Open the cabinet door on the left, place the pepper shaker inside the cabinet in front of the lotion bottle, and close the door.
Turn around and face the counter with the gray bowl and pepper shakers.
Pick up the pepper shaker that's behind the gray bowl.
Turn around and face the cabinets below the counter.
Open the cabinet door on the left side, place the pepper shaker in the cabinet to the left of the first pepper shaker, and close the door.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the small table with a gray top.
Pick up the third salt shaker in the middle.
Turn around and take the salt shaker to the cabinet below the drawers.
Place the salt shaker inside the cabinet.
Turn around and go back to the table with salt shakers.
Take the salt shaker next to the green apple.
Turn around and go back to the cabinet below the drawers.
Place the salt shaker left of the first shaker.
anns.task_desc: Take the salt shakers from the table to the cabinet.
